latestIgtvVideos.title: Beach Day/ Golden Hour Makeup Look☀️
SUN TAN REMOVAL REMEDY FOR MEN & WOMEN BOTH!🤩
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
1. Take 2-3 oranges, peel them off and dry them up for atleast 5 days. 
2. Then grind the peels to form a scrub texture.
3. Store the scrub powder in an airtight jar. (It remains fresh for atleast 2 months) 
4. Take 1 tbspn powder and add some honey or oil according to your skin type. ( People with oily skin shouldn't opt for oil, use honey instead! & People with dry or combination skin can use both according to your comfort ) 
5. Scrub it gently on the tanned areas of your body. 
6. Keep it for 15-20 minutes & rinse it off with normal water.
7. Do not forget to moisturise your skin after scrubbing!!
•PS- Use this remedy for 2-3 times a week to mark the difference!• .
.
.
.
.
